Ansible - Configurtion management tool - mainly Infrastructure automation tool - solves issue with deploying & managing servers effeciently, reliably 
Allows to write infrastructure as code and save it in the repository - writing code allows to test the code script if its resulting in desired state - also allows easy & quick roll back to the previous state.
Agentless architecture.

Features : 
  1. Idempotent - configures the infrastuture in the same desired state every single time its run.
  2. Orchestration - allows to make the changes to infra in an order. 
  
Installing Ansible :
  1. Dependencies : Works over SSH protocol, requires Python to run
  2. To install ansible : pip install ansible
  3. To check if installed : ansible --version 
  
